                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-01-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 13, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Conger acknowledges Department’s telegram of the 10th instant, and requests
                    instructions concerning indemnities, an approximate estimate of war
                    expenditures, and wishes as to revision of the treaties.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
